78
00:04:36,978 --> 00:04:40,313
Yo, where are you going?
The car's this way.

79
00:04:40,347 --> 00:04:41,816
Police! Freeze!

80
00:04:41,849 --> 00:04:42,984
Drop your weap...

81
00:04:43,017 --> 00:04:44,986
