104
00:06:02,129 --> 00:06:03,798
Help me, James.

105
00:06:03,831 --> 00:06:06,000
[tires screech, squeal]

106
00:06:06,033 --> 00:06:07,702
Watch out, watch out!

107
00:06:10,538 --> 00:06:12,673
[tires screech]

108
00:06:13,841 --> 00:06:15,543
[partner groaning]

109
00:06:16,143 --> 00:06:19,412
Knight, help me.

110
00:06:19,446 --> 00:06:21,616
[siren approaching]

111
