[siren stops]

112
00:06:31,792 --> 00:06:33,160
[ambulance door slams]

113
00:06:49,176 --> 00:06:51,411
[people chattering]

114
00:06:58,019 --> 00:07:00,054
[plane engine whirring]

115
00:07:18,539 --> 00:07:20,041
Casey, can we talk about
what happened?

116
00:07:20,808 --> 00:07:23,210
I didn't sign up
to shoot cops, man.

117
00:07:24,045 --> 00:07:26,147
The whole FBI
is probably chasing us by now.

118
00:07:29,216 --> 00:07:30,785
It was us or them.

119
00:07:30,818 --> 00:07:33,654
That cop did his job,
we did ours.

120
00:07:33,688 --> 00:07:36,991
We did it better on the day.
For what? A couple grand?

121
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:43,097
Uh, six, seven, eight, minus
Winna's cut. So, that's, uh, 134K.

122
00:07:44,198 --> 00:07:45,465
134?

123
