130
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:15,663
You told me to take care of it,
so I took care of it.

131
00:08:15,696 --> 00:08:18,165
Besides, you're the one
who shot the fucking cop.

132
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:20,101
