137
00:08:30,344 --> 00:08:32,279
Whoa, whoa. What's your point?

138
00:08:32,313 --> 00:08:33,981
You not only
put my life in danger,

139
00:08:34,015 --> 00:08:36,650
you tried to screw over
our fucking teammates.

140
00:08:36,684 --> 00:08:38,886
Do you think I don't have
your fucking back?

141
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:41,088
Huh?
Is that what you're saying?

142
00:08:41,122 --> 00:08:43,758
You're the one coming to me,
"Oh, my knee is busted.

143
00:08:43,791 --> 00:08:45,760
Oh, shit.
Give me some fucking pills.

144
00:08:45,793 --> 00:08:48,329
Oh, come practice with me so I
can make a fucking comeback.

145
00:08:48,362 --> 00:08:51,165
Oh, my life is over." Huh?
Who had your fucking back then?

146
00:08:51,198 --> 00:08:53,801
You asked me to go,
and I fucking go.

147
00:08:53,834 --> 00:08:55,236
Fuck you, Casey.

148
00:08:56,704 --> 00:08:58,606
You know I'm not in this
for the money.

149
00:09:01,842 --> 00:09:03,944
[engine whirring]

150
00:09:06,981 --> 00:09:08,716
[staff chattering]

151
