167
00:11:14,308 --> 00:11:17,311
Yeah. All right, I'll get
Mercer's cut to him.

168
00:11:17,344 --> 00:11:18,345
[Casey] Thank you.

169
00:11:18,379 --> 00:11:21,315
138K. This is Winna's cut.

170
00:11:21,348 --> 00:11:22,449
Hey, Case.

171
00:11:23,751 --> 00:11:25,419
